metadata.name: MS-OS Salt
metadata.description:
A simulated soul, finding themselves back in the real world, in Anchor City, remains bewildered about their place in all things. Blurring realities again, they undergo a new journey.

The alchemical process of the body and soul is a mysterious one. You can only know if you start the journey yourself. It will be magical,it will be dark. It will be adventurous, it will be boring. Hot and cold, light and shadow. All the prism of emotions, all elements of creation through time and space, held in a timeless way and an open heart. Shunyi is one with the caring process.
